1:1 COMMENT "# string_codepoints.z -- Phase S5 codepoint iteration + count."
1:63 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# `count` returns the codepoint count (O(n) UTF-8 walk); differs"
3:65 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# from `length`, which returns byte count."
4:43 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# `codepoints` returns an iterator yielding one u32 codepoint per"
5:66 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# .call. Ill-formed bytes are replaced with U+FFFD."
6:52 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "#"
7:2 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# Uses ASCII for the live test (static-literal UTF-8 emission has"
8:66 EOL "\n"
9:1 COMMENT "# a known upstream double-encoding bug for non-ASCII literals)."
9:64 EOL "\n"
10:1 EOL "\n"
